Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.41,0:02:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Hue is in a critical state.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Crime Coefficient is still fluctuating, but it's possible it could worsen rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:25.87,Psychotitle,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\shad2\fad(500,300)\c&HE7E8D1&\alpha&H30&\1a&H00&\pos(313,60.667)}#19: Transparent Shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't address your clouded Hue,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,if worst comes to worst, you could be declared a latent criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered how my partner ended up in the same situation long ago.{>partner}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not my partner anymore.{gripping dialogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one of my subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ironic.{like 10,000 spoons when all you need is a knife}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trying my best not to end up like him, and yet, this is how it all turns out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll set up an intensive therapy program for you immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll also notify your office—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ginoza...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll manage to get by, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you want, but I won't be responsible for what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My current colleague... is a young woman who was hired this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching her gives me hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me feel that everything depends on how you look at the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Saiga...{Get in the car}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're even carrying a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,An old revolver... Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you're psychic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you this many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a simple matter of observation and logical thinking, Kougami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you all know this by now, but Kougami has escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll probably go after Makishima. We will too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you encounter the fugitive Enforcer, take care of him immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're to capture Makishima alive, but shoot Kougami on sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we put Kougami aside for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're bound to run into him if we drive Makishima into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Makishima is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an ID on his face,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:05:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but parts of the monitoring system are still undergoing repairs in the wake of the riots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be five days before it's completely operational again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, we won't be able to rely on facial recognition to help us investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think Makishima will use that time to try and escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No. He's bound to make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That man isn't the type to give up just because he's been cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's compelled to test this world until his dying breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll confront this society, protected as it is by the System, with blunt human nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Makishima Shougo made that provocative call to Kougami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... This isn't the time to feel depressed, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be a saint, but I'm all yours if you need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I haven't vented at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami...{makes my heart go dokidoki}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want him to cross the line from latent criminal to murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what else happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't shoulder everything all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay. If you're worried, would you like to check my Hue?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised when I checked it myself this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after everything that's happened, it's a pale turquoise color.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how cold-hearted must I be?{more like, just how dense}{how the fuck did you make it through detective school, girl?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your heart and your Psycho-Pass are two separate things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what does that make a Psycho-Pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is... a person's heart?{what is love? baby don't hurt me, don't hurt me, no more}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? You didn't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having too much trouble predicting what Makishima's next move could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So you think that man is going to do something more?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The security network in the metropolitan area will be fully restored in five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the CID's analyst told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To Makishima, that's how long he has to launch his last fireworks display.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I made some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made from real coffee beans, so it's pretty damn strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked through the information you brought with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see why you're having trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your assessment of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's such a thing as political offenders in this society managed by the Sibyl System,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,this man would be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrorists, anarchists, agitators,{damn, that breakfast looks fucking delicious}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,suicidal revolutionaries with no interest in the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not a decent man among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what would you say is the definition of anarchism?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a denial of government and authority,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but different from flat-out chaos and disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about denying an inhuman control system and building a more human system.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Makishima is close to being an anarchist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but since he delights so much in destruction, he's somewhat different to the original meaning of the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,An inhuman control system... Sibyl, then?{well, not exactly...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to borrow Max Weber's words,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,ideal bureaucrats are those who intently perform their duty without anger or fondness,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:09:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,without hate or zeal, and without love or personal predilection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In that sense, the Sibyl System may be close to the ideal bureaucratic administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's assuming that all the details we know about Sibyl are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Makishima told me on the phone that he came to know the true form of Sibyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it wasn't something worth putting my life on the line to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me quote a little more from Max Weber.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bureaucratic administration dominates the people through knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Technical knowledge and practical knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping that knowledge increases their superiority.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Makishima is trying to strip that superiority away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And he almost succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Those riots pushed society right up to a very dangerous line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Ministry of Welfare made some sort of proposal to Makishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he refused that proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk to this Makishima guy sometime in a session recorded on video or audio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,For your research?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't interest me in that way yet.{gaaaaaaay}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be purely to help your investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If Makishima was here right now, how do you think he'd join our conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He would...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,probably respond by quoting Foucault or Jeremy Bentham the moment you quoted Max Weber.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really a "system"? Or more like a huge prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The Panopticon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A facility that allows you to observe everyone at once. Sibyl is its worst possible form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can control the maximum number of prisoners with the minimum number of guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He might even quote Gulliver's Travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a cynical man with a distorted sense of humor.{lolfuni}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So he lampoons science and politics that have become too advanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's that kind of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you a personal question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you consider yourself and Makishima to be alike?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some aspects of him that I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about his past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But one thing I'm certain of is that there was a critical turning point in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment he realized that he was idiosyncratic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He can control his Psycho-Pass at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people would probably consider that a privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But Makishima didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What he felt was... probably a sense of alienation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In this society, if the Sibyl System doesn't acknowledge you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't that essentially the same as not being recognized as a human being?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A child who wasn't accepted into the group...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Maybe that's where it all began.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That being said, this is all just speculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't know the truth unless we ask Makishima himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're not going to ask him, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're done here, come to my study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hence, the ones who know Kougami Shinya's personality and way of thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and are most suited to predict his pattern of actions are us at CID Division 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So how did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Our orders remain unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:13:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We, Division 1, will continue to work toward tracking down Kougami and Makishima Shougo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You and the young lady should both stop concerning yourselves with those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be Division 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do it, maybe we can convince Kougami to surrender before we have to shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Nobuchika...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you become so soft?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Ko surrenders, he'll probably be thrown into a facility and executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we go after Kougami Shinya, we have no choice but to put our lives on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That being the case, why don't we leave it to Division 3 and—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And make it someone else's problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you also realized what Kougami was thinking and just let him be, right?!{hug it out, boys}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you didn't even try to stop him! You just waved goodbye as he walked out the door, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So that he'd kill Makishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's clearly a breach of trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A criminal act, even!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what excuses you make, you can't deceive the Dominators!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to check your Crime Coefficient right here and now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!{nigga.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody leaves me behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and just heads on over to the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you and Kougami want to be heroes that badly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about justice. It's an obsession.{It's not about justice. This time I just like girls.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you know there are other, wiser ways to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you feel that if you turn your back on everything you've worked toward, it's like admitting you lived a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had moments like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is all because of your pride as Enforcers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not because we're Enforcers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is because of our pride as men.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I have my own pride as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll capture that idiot Kougami with my own hands at any cost, no matter what anyone says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But under the current circumstances, there's no one immediately available to use as our pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the final, collective decision by everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't fully understand with my current capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to go back there once and check the consensus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an old type anonymous message board.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's operated via several overseas servers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Overseas servers?{??????????????}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you look in the right places, you can find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, they've managed to stay out of the Sibyl System's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:16:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The users of this board are former college professors, journalists, critics, literary scholars...{in the future, all the smartest people will gather on 4chan}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the people who the Sibyl System determined were useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They still comment even now as their frustration builds up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,saying things like, "there's nothing good about Sibyl," or "this part is so problematic."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It might ultimately be fruitless, but it's better to at least have somewhere to act as an outlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I started a thread before breakfast.
