Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They responded to my thread as though it were an interesting game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They all look like stupid jokes to me.{damn shitposters}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then pick whichever joke you think is funniest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Makishima are alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust your inspiration.
