Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.58,0:17:06.04,lt,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur0.8\c&HD7E642&\b1\fscx66\fscy66\pos(288,176)}{TS 17:15} If it's not possible to break into the system,\N\N\N I think a good approach is to start by breaking things that surround it.
