Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.58,0:17:06.04,lt,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur0.8\fscx66\fscy66\c&HD7E642&\b1\pos(288,484)}{TS 17:16} To cause a collapse of the Sibyl System,\N\N\N wouldn't the best way to be to destroy the food autonomy system?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:06.04,lt,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3.8\fscx66\fscy66\c&HD7E642&\b1\pos(288,484)\alpha&H80&}{TS 17:16} To cause a collapse of the Sibyl System,\N\N\N wouldn't the best way to be to destroy the food autonomy system?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Something caught my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What if the Sibyl System collapsed due to a food shortage?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyper-oats...{nigga what}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}99% of the food currently consumed in this country is processed food made from hyper-oats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're oats that have been genetically modified for maximum harvest efficiency.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Currently, we depend solely on this single item.{soylent green: the anime}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An enormous amount of a "monospecific genus" that eliminates diversity, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see... If a single fatal defect was found, it's possible that they could be completely wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be Makishima's next target.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Food self-sufficiency, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. This might be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Crops, production systems, genetic modification...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have information on any of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the sharp decline in population and the completion of the Sibyl System,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it became impossible to restrain the excess density of settlement in urban areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But while people can be relocated, land cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The primary industry of agriculture was forced to shift to complete automation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Through mechanized farming by Drones,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,genetically enhanced hyper-oats, and disease countermeasures using benign viruses,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,we were able to achieve fully automated farming, eliminating agricultural workers from this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the Hokuriku area is a vast granary with zero population.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are any problems with crop health management,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,hyper-oats, being a monospecific genus, will be devastated by disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:19:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And if the food autonomy system collapses, Japan will have to once again import food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The government will once again be forced to open communications with other countries.{makishima shougo = commodore perry. you heard it here first}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As food shortages sweep the nation, the entire Japanese population's Crime Coefficients will rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But once they lift the ban on food importation,\N they'll have no choice but to relax border security.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Refugees will probably start to flow into the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Once that happens, the very measurement of \NCrime Coefficients might become meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So what else does he require?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, Makishima needs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,an expert's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I knowingly took part in your plan to kill Makishima Shougo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And since my actions were deliberate, the next time I get a surprise check, that'll be it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry to have put you through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:20:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is simply my punishment for shutting myself up at home and not participating in society.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,By assisting you, I feel that I've fulfilled my own role. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,even so, Kougami...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dumping all the dirty work on you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you definitely shouldn't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I can't even imagine someone else besides me killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inspector Tsunemori Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tell you the truth behind everything.{oh boy}
